title: GoPro: HERO5 - Video Stabilization
description:
HERO5 Black can capture stunningly smooth wide-angle video  handheld or mounted to your favorite vehicles, gear and more.

As always, happy capturing!

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of GoPro HERO5 Action Cameras with Video Stabilization. Shop for the full line of GoPro Action Cams at Abt today!

You might see examples of extreme use in this video. Please take appropriate precautions to ensure your own safety and the safety of those around you, and to protect your GoPro camera.
